Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.92,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you know？　身の程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.96,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes, I know！　高いプライド
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.84,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}What you want？　言いなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.30,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All I want！Only you！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:04.09,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,どんなやり込み要素を盛り込んでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.06,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,思い込みが過ぎてるでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.10,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,こうじゃないと言いたいハッピーエンド
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.73,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}意味不明の世迷い言を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.06,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空想だった感情が現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.57,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Ah！Cool！ You’re cool！Beautiful！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:22.28,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}平穏だった日常が乱雑に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.57,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t believe！ You have to leave！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.62,OP-JP W,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,10)\fad(200,200)}好きも
