Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:12.99,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:14.12,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord2.44\blur4\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\fs108\3c&HAC9379&\4c&HBD6BFA&\4a&HFF&\frz5.89\pos(1018,908)\fsp24}无论是谁
